response.original_title: Sesame Street: Elmo’s Holiday Spectacular: The Nutcracker and Other Tales
response.overview: The holidays are here on Sesame Street! Join Elmo, his puppy Tango, and all their friends on adventures filled with music, magic, and so much more! Play, sing, and explore in this two-hour holiday spectacular. Little ones will meet a reindeer-in-training named Lightning, explore magical lands with Abby Cadabby and Cookie Monster, and try and save Christmas with Elmo!
response.title: Sesame Street: Elmo’s Holiday Spectacular: The Nutcracker and Other Tales
